Second Regular Session

Parliament Resolution No. **300**

**Principally Authored by:**

MP Baintan A. Ampatuan, MP Michael E. Midtimbang, MP, Diamila D. Ramos, MP Sittie Fahanie S. Uy-Oyod, MP Rasul Y. Mitmug, MP Suharto M. Ambolodto, MP Tawakal B. Midtimbang, MP Bassor D. Utto, MP Mudjib C. Abu, MP Mohammad Kelie U. Antao, MP Suwaib L. Oranan

**Co-Authored by:**

MP Jaafar Apollo Mikhail L. Matalam, MP Susana S. Anayatin, MP Atty. Randolph C. Parcasio, MP Albakil D. Jikiri,

**RESOLUTION CONGRATULATING FORMER CONGRESSMAN MOHAMMED HUSSEIN P. PANGANDAMAN FOR HIS APPOINTMENT AS ADMINISTRATOR OF THE AUTHORITY OF THE FREEPORT AREA OF BATAAN (AFAB)**

**Whereas,** Mohammed Hussein P. Pangandaman is a seasoned politician who served as Congressman of the 1st District of Lanao del Sur; and Whereas, Mohammed Hussein P. Pangandaman displayed exceptional leadership skills during his term as Congressman, actively advocating for the welfare of his constituents and passing several bills effectively addressing key concerns affecting his district; and

**Whereas,** Mohammed Hussein P. Pangandaman was recently appointed by President Ferdinand “Bong bong” R. Marcos Jr. as the Administrator of the Authority of the Freeport Area of Bataan (AFAB), which is tasked with promoting economic growth through the establishment of a world-class freeport area in Bataan; and

**Whereas,** Mohammed Hussein P. Pangandaman's extensive political experience, coupled with his outstanding track record of leadership, positions him as an excellent candidate for the said position, and his appointment is commendable.

**Therefore, be it resolved,** that we the Bangsamoro Parliament congratulates former Congressman Mohammed Hussein P. Pangandaman on his appointment as Administrator of the Authority of the Freeport Area of Bataan (AFAB).

Adopted this ____ day of the month of ____ in the year of ____,

